52
00:06:48,170 --> 00:06:49,980
You mustn't die!

53
00:07:01,930 --> 00:07:03,550
Sorry.

54
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,140
I love you.

55
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:13,820
I love you, Kurono-kun.

