when you weren't home.

317
00:34:50,850 --> 00:34:52,100
Try it.

318
00:34:52,350 --> 00:34:54,480
You're the first person I made it for.

319
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:18,480
This is Kojima.

320
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:23,100
