324
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:37,260
I want to see you.

325
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:40,610
Can I go to your workplace right now?

326
00:35:47,370 --> 00:35:50,950
[Kojima Tae]

327
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:58,550
[Kojima Tae]

