442
01:03:31,830 --> 01:03:35,470
[Nakamura]
[0 point]

443
01:03:33,170 --> 01:03:37,540
Yamamoto, Ayukawa, you, and I...

444
01:03:38,650 --> 01:03:41,760
We defeated these aliens dressed in black...

445
01:03:42,490 --> 01:03:44,410
