493
01:09:58,220 --> 01:09:59,130
Thank you very much.

494
01:10:00,980 --> 01:10:02,060
Thank you very much!

495
01:10:03,430 --> 01:10:05,310
Ah, it's nothing.

496
01:10:07,600 --> 01:10:10,710
